Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.86,0:00:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你是厕所里的花子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:18.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小广是笨蛋 我再也不理你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.05,0:00:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鵺野老师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.91,0:00:23.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你好好体会自己的无力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.18,0:00:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.22,0:00:26.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这世上存在着肉眼无法看见的黑暗住人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.94,0:01:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们偶尔也会显露獠牙 袭击你们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.26,0:01:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是为从它们手中保护你们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.84,0:01:15.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从地狱深渊前来的 正义使者…也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.46,0:01:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鵺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.22,0:02:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要收集来那么多材料应该就没有问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.55,0:02:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一定会大吃一惊的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学园创立祭的节目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.63,0:03:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们五年三班一定独领风骚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一定是第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好好推嘛小诚 东西很重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经手软了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:12.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 我们休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.16,0:03:14.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里刚好有一块石头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里是让旅人坐下来休息的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.66,0:03:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅人?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:21.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里以前是大街
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.49,0:03:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以有很多旅人从这个地方通过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过听说现在只有幽灵出没了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会嘛 那只是传说而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出 出现了...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鵺 快点收伏他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.02,0:03:50.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们好像是过去的旅人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.51,0:03:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人并不是幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.65,0:03:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是石头的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.05,0:03:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是幽灵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.08,0:03:59.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.25,0:04:04.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东西都会留有记忆的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.56,0:04:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是像这种年代久远的石头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.88,0:04:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石头的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.63,0:04:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓了我一大跳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前的记忆可以像录像带一样重新播放出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪全明星总登场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.17,0:04:22.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被诅咒的学园祭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.64,0:04:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种令人食指大动的味道 无法抗拒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.16,0:04:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.83,0:04:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样子比较好吃哦 鵺野老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.78,0:04:52.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个好吃吗 冰冻的章鱼烧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.76,0:04:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来喂你吃好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.57,0:05:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 鵺野老师 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.35,0:05:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学园祭好像很好玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.19,0:05:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,童守小学的成立纪念日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以学生跟老师同心协力一起举行学园祭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.97,0:05:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成立纪念的学园祭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚好可以让我们约会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:18.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么约会 这是学校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可不可以离我远点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.84,0:05:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 老师竟然害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:26.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有占卜摊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.54,0:05:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,占卜?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去算一下命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很糟糕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.67,0:05:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你千万要小心一点才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我该小心哪一方面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.22,0:05:43.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的命理显示你会遭受女难
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还蛮准的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.23,0:05:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遭受女难?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是女人会给他带来很多的麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 占卜费五百元
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.30,0:05:54.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个算命师真没礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.48,0:05:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五百元太贵了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三百元就好了 好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:05:59.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五百元就是五百元
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管狐?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:04.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.15,0:06:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊津奈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了 阿鵺老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跑到这个地方来做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.59,0:06:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看了就知道 我在占卜打工嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:16.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这个月手头很紧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:20.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这个样子也不能随便跑到学校来赚钱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到了没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:26.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 有什么了不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得我还那么诚心想拜他为师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.62,0:06:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不干了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:35.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天都要跟你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.84,0:06:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦 会被大家看见的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.20,0:06:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.62,0:06:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是老师哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:41.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:42.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:48.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也许很受欢迎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.90,0:06:53.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们跑过头了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.98,0:06:56.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.15,0:06:58.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好想见你 玉藻老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:03.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是那个臭玉藻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 你好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.72,0:07:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.03,0:07:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久没来这个学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.47,0:07:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.09,0:07:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帅什么帅嘛 那个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.44,0:07:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然老师你还是我一个人的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是学校啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.14,0:07:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们感情很好嘛 鵺野君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,校长先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:25.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我未婚夫一直很受您照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:26.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们什么时候结婚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.77,0:07:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 校长先生你开什么玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.15,0:07:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说真的 每一个班上的摊位都很别出心裁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:44.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.16,0:07:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们班也很努力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.52,0:07:49.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 五年三班做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是鬼屋探险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.22,0:07:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有鵺野老师班上的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.36,0:08:03.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼 鬼屋探险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道你一定做这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.66,0:08:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有点过时了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.24,0:08:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 这也没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:12.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是鵺野老师的班嘛 对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用那么说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:18.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 我们到里面去参观一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:20.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的仿真度很高的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:23.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为一直都看着真家伙 水准很高哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.99,0:08:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好黑哦 什么都看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好怨恨哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.13,0:08:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎你们来到阿鵺班上的鬼屋探险
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是独眼小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.41,0:08:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是河童
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要吸光你的血
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.55,0:09:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是妖猫哦 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑什么啊 阿鵺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.81,0:09:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是一些骗小孩的鬼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.67,0:09:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们平常也常看到真鬼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:18.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是没有模仿力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下子变成搞笑屋了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.46,0:09:24.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 你太失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.57,0:09:26.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是那么的拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鵺 你太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕 你们装得真像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:33.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好怕 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在才说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.73,0:09:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想搂在一起而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.48,0:09:38.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好好 出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.88,0:09:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 害我没干劲了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.72,0:09:46.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个鬼屋也是大家精心设计出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.78,0:09:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 这个座敷娃娃不是也扮得很像吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:51.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又没有化妆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.73,0:09:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直是栩栩如生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.37,0:09:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要理阿鵺了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.52,0:10:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的惹他们生气了 这下糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.42,0:10:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 你也在鬼屋里扮一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.25,0:10:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮助下我的学生们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:06.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来绝对会很恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 真是个好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.49,0:10:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.77,0:10:12.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不是什么妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.72,0:10:14.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是真正的雪女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不关我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.61,0:10:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 你太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也不关我的事...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.11,0:10:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很好玩的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小学生拽什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.81,0:10:38.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥 要不要过去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.68,0:10:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.87,0:10:43.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也让我们好好开心一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.19,0:10:47.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种东西也敢拿给我们吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.89,0:10:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自以为是的学园祭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.86,0:10:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们走着瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别挡路 别挡路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里有占卜摊哦 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.82,0:11:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很好玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.33,0:11:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我要收摊了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.54,0:11:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不帮我们算命吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.43,0:11:18.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要小看我们大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点帮我占卜 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.36,0:11:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 五百元哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:30.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就给你五百元
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会碰到很恐怖的经验
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖的经验啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.78,0:11:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且面相还显示你会有水难
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.25,0:11:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么有水难嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:44.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你少在那边乌鸦嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:46.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五百元拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.28,0:11:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这种骗人的半仙还敢跟我要钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.20,0:11:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说啊 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.86,0:11:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们一定会有报应的 到时候我不管你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.97,0:12:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪兽来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.67,0:12:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要做这种无聊的事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就没有什么好玩的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.65,0:12:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们看 那边有鬼屋哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.94,0:12:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然已经过时了 不过看起来好像还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.23,0:12:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该很好玩的样子 就让我们玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.66,0:12:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要五十元啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.17,0:12:35.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是贵了点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.39,0:12:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.24,0:12:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这是优待价
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:43.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很恐怖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.56,0:12:46.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的 我觉得很恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不恐怖我会发飙的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.91,0:12:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿去 五十元
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.19,0:12:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不行啦 一个人五十元
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么关系嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.43,0:12:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有客人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.76,0:13:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作 工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备 OK
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.69,0:13:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼先生啊 你们在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么搞的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.88,0:13:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好怨恨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.42,0:13:23.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭你也想吓我再过个十年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过三十年再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.51,0:13:31.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我这个吸血鬼活生生的把你的血吸光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的会吸血吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.97,0:13:38.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点也不恐怖嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.06,0:13:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.09,0:13:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩的玩意儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.71,0:13:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.78,0:13:47.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.08,0:13:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 叫我们住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.30,0:13:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我就是叫你住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.78,0:13:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些都是我们努力做出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.11,0:13:59.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你凭什么来破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.93,0:14:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊 太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太过分了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.97,0:14:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们太乱来了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.17,0:14:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.37,0:14:10.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也是付了五十元进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是客人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.68,0:14:15.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他骗人 他们三个人总共才付了五十元
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.39,0:14:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们每天都留下来做到很晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.66,0:14:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.90,0:14:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭小鬼 少瞧不起人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.10,0:14:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得那么粗糙的鬼还敢收人家的钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.06,0:14:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.53,0:14:37.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你不甘心就拿像样一点的鬼出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.16,0:14:39.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们真的吓破胆的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.75,0:14:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们那些人好过分哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.75,0:14:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鵺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.54,0:14:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都乱七八糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.93,0:14:58.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我们打不过高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 那些混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.44,0:15:02.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不甘心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.14,0:15:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.57,0:15:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小小的人类竟然敢看不起妖怪 我要你们好看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.47,0:15:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉藻 我先跟你说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我跟我的学生们的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会让你插手管的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鵺野老师...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.08,0:15:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样也好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.44,0:15:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就让我好好领教你的高招了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小广
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那几个家伙说就拿像样一点的鬼出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.56,0:15:41.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.34,0:15:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是让他们真的吓破胆的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是这么说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.35,0:15:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:49.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然这样我就让他们如愿以偿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.29,0:15:53.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢把大家辛苦劳动成果践踏成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会放过他们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.54,0:15:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鵺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:57.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鵺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:05.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 阿鵺班上真正的鬼屋探险现在正式登场了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.68,0:16:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙天地 興我力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.53,0:16:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,降伏群魔 迎来曙光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.34,0:16:17.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾人左手 所封百鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:20.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尊我号令 只在此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们才不要喝果汁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿啤酒来 啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:35.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可是客人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.73,0:16:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.48,0:16:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫你们拿啤酒来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:40.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不知道已经给大家添麻烦了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.22,0:16:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你们马上给我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个小妞生起气来更性感了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陪我们兄弟几个喝酒作乐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快出去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.23,0:16:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我 放开我 不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:16:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊来啊 来陪我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:16:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么 别出那种怪声音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那个小鬼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:04.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找我们干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.56,0:17:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的鬼屋探险又重新开张了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.45,0:17:09.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一次可是真正像样的鬼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我敢拍胸脯保证一定不会让你们失望的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:24.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 跟刚才一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.96,0:17:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次是免费的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.47,0:17:27.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:29.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是特地来玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.92,0:17:36.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次要是又不恐怖的话 那该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.67,0:17:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都做好心理准备了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.52,0:17:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还会弄个稀烂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.84,0:17:42.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该做心理准备的人是你们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 请进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.75,0:17:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.97,0:17:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪有什么可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么突然觉得有点阵阵阴风的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.86,0:17:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一定是心理作用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.05,0:17:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是好像有点阴森森啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.31,0:18:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.95,0:18:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才好像没有那个东西的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.86,0:18:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可原谅 不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.84,0:18:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罪人们全都要砍下脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.44,0:18:16.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这到底怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.72,0:18:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要砍头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.14,0:18:26.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砍头砍头 我要砍头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.09,0:18:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.61,0:18:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是怎么动的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我吃掉你的心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.42,0:18:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在后悔已经太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:50.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鵺已经叫出真正的鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.47,0:18:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不吓到昏倒可是出不去的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.35,0:18:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一定都是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼 开门开门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:55.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放我们出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.56,0:18:58.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼赶快开门 把门打开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.40,0:19:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千万不要小看阿鵺班哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.67,0:19:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定你们不能活着出去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.76,0:19:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是那个装妖猫的小鬼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.22,0:19:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那里做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.76,0:19:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在等你们 伸着脖子等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:17.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长脖子女妖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.48,0:19:20.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要过来 救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.74,0:19:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.53,0:19:54.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些不是机关
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.01,0:19:57.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算做梦也该醒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.57,0:20:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受够了 我们快点逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.18,0:20:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这个把人头砍下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.58,0:20:10.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,运用杠杆原理 就像剥虾皮一样把头骨剥出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.91,0:20:12.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.24,0:20:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.28,0:20:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.19,0:20:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.60,0:20:20.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.27,0:20:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总 总算得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.93,0:20:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这里是厕所啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:33.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚好 我想要小便
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也快要尿裤子了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.66,0:20:36.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是没用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,门打不开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.16,0:20:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,门打不开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.34,0:20:53.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,门打不开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.21,0:20:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是花子 救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.00,0:21:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 那么没出息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.63,0:21:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.27,0:21:09.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是说要拿点像样的让你们吓破胆的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.02,0:21:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们刚才看到的不是真鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:13.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.85,0:21:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个水晶石保留的石头的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.58,0:21:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个东西的灵力是很强的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.49,0:21:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它可以把那个记忆鲜明的重新显现出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.93,0:21:24.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像看录像带一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.49,0:21:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种恐怖的学校我下次不敢来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.35,0:21:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一等 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.03,0:21:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.13,0:21:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙夹着尾巴逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.12,0:21:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大成功
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.36,0:21:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 阿鵺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鵺老师 真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.78,0:21:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个主意不错 鵺野老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.21,0:21:44.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 你好帅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.83,0:21:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样嘛 雪女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.83,0:21:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的占卜术也很厉害嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.29,0:21:50.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然失禁了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.83,0:21:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连他们会遭水难都被我说中了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.05,0:21:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我都跟你说了 怎么还在打工赚钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.16,0:22:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.68,0:22:04.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鵺老师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.02,0:22:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是关心我所以才会常常骂我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.76,0:22:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好高兴 我最喜欢你了 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.04,0:22:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花心萝卜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.23,0:22:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦 这不是...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.23,0:22:18.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.13,0:22:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会原谅你的 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.87,0:22:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原谅我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.08,0:22:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.09,0:22:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说他遭女难也说中了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.67,0:22:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说不饶你就是不饶你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.90,0:22:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要跑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.90,0:24:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.37,0:24:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二宫金次郎的石像追着我跑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.77,0:24:13.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎么样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.61,0:24:16.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是背上背着柴 手上拿着本书的石像
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.60,0:24:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说石像会动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.20,0:24:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还追着你跑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.73,0:24:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 他用跑的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.22,0:24:25.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想他一定是袭击不喜欢念书的孩子的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.69,0:24:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地狱老师阿鵺
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.38,0:24:28.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放学后的恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.66,0:24:30.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奔跑的二宫金次郎石像
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.73,0:24:33.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 石像真的在跑啊
